descriptionHtml:
Browse the internet securely with the Research Web browser.

Research Web Browser Features:
◼ Private browser provides User-friendly interface. Block annoying ads. Experience productive and smooth Web browsing. The ideal browser for research.

📥 Smart File Download System
A highly advanced tool for video download, image download and audio download.

🕵️‍♂️ Safe Browsing
Surf websites as if no one is watching you. Your searches, cookies are not saved in the Research Web browser. Also, keep your browsing history private by using a secure tab.

🔎 Smart Search
With smart search suggestions, you get a fast and relevant search. Also, the most used Web sites are listed for you.

🔋 Battery and Data Saver
Research crawler shortens page load speed. Protects you from advertisements infected with malware. It increases the performance of the Web page. Optimized for your device to use less charge.

🧬 Research Browser
Discover new information. Read news, listen to music. Watch video. Surf the Unlimited Web world.
